questions.quote: Please! Are you kidding? I-I hurt three huge men, I gave a guy a bloody nose-I mean I-I'm not proud of it but, I really am. And it's all because of you, wonderful, amazing you.
On Melanie Griffith in "Working girl". I think what you want is over here.
You're Elizabeth's father, huh? I can see now where she gets her rugged handsomeness.
Oh thanks, but listen, I was just at Monica's and she and Chandler had a big fight and they're not moving in.
Oh, what about that guy over there? Remember? That is the guy you flirted with at the counter that time.
Alright, Monica dear, I'm gonna hit the road. Now I've left my 10 verbs on the table. And you be sure and send me that finished poem.
All right, there's a nuclear holocaust, I'm the last man on Earth. Would you go out with me?
